    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158650/extras/a8c54984803b42b9f71a304e3accc1b2.poster.avif?t=1767708859\" width=800 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158650/extras/a8c54984803b42b9f71a304e3accc1b2.webm?t=1767708859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158650/extras/a8c54984803b42b9f71a304e3accc1b2.mp4?t=1767708859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>为了给素未谋面的逝者哭灵，坎德拉里亚从一个葬礼奔赴另一个葬礼，她决定连夜跋涉以避免失眠。<br><br>明明没买任何票，她却摸到了一张神秘的暗光线巴士票。登上巴士后，她不得不面对来自过去的心理创伤，并为自己的人生定下一个新目标。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158650/extras/a8c54984803b42b9f71a304e3accc1b2.poster.avif?t=1767708859\" width=800 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158650/extras/a8c54984803b42b9f71a304e3accc1b2.webm?t=1767708859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158650/extras/a8c54984803b42b9f71a304e3accc1b2.mp4?t=1767708859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >巴士行程</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>体验一个氛围感十足的短篇故事，该故事由屡获殊荣的Tiago Rech撰写，他的代表作有《TELEFORUM》《Dodgeball Academia》《No Place for Bravery》以及《Galaxy of Pen &amp; Paper》。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你的终点站会是何处？做出不同选择，找到5种以上结局。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在4K分辨率下观赏一种独特而又黑暗的艺术风格。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在一场超现实的旅程中，与古怪的乘客们进行互动。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>奔赴不同葬礼，为逝者哭灵。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在创伤中找寻……或永远逃避自我。</li></ul>",
